<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>884</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ wǒ zūn suì nǐ, yīn nǐ wěi dà. zhǔ wǒ tóu kào nǐ, yīn nǐ xìn shí.
 zhǔ wǒ kào jìn nǐ, yīn nǐ cí ài. shì nǐ gěi wǒ yǒng héng de shēng mìng. nǐ shì
 wǒ yī shēng de zhěng jiù, wǒ yī shēng de pàn wàng. cǐ shí cǐ kè wǒ yào kāi kǒu gē chàng,
 sī xiǎng nǐ de cí ài gèng shì nán wàng. wǒ yào bǎ nǐ de míng chuán yáng sì fāng.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ wǒ zūn suì nǐ 迦南884</title>
</song>